  },
  {
    question: "What makes Decatur a good short-term rental market?",
    answer: "Decatur offers unique short-term rental opportunities with Wheeler Lake recreation (fishing, boating, camping), Point Mallard Water Park and campground visitors, Tennessee River attractions, historic downtown, and proximity to Huntsville. The area attracts outdoor enthusiasts year-round."
  },
  {
    question: "How quickly can you turn over a property?",
    answer: "Most Decatur properties can be turned over in 2-3 hours depending on size and condition. For same-day turnovers, book in advance to ensure availability. We understand tight check-in/check-out windows and work efficiently."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you service vacation rentals near Wheeler Lake?",
    answer: "Yes! We serve lake houses and vacation rentals near Wheeler Lake, along the Tennessee River, and throughout the Point Mallard area. These properties often need extra attention for sand, fishing gear, and outdoor activity debris."
  },
  {
    question: "Can you handle last-minute turnover requests?",
    answer: "We try our best! While advance booking is preferred, we understand the nature of short-term rentals. Call us as soon as you know about a same-day turnover and we'll do everything possible to accommodate you."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you restock supplies and toiletries?",
    answer: "Yes! If you provide supplies, we'll restock them during turnover. We can also purchase and restock supplies for you at cost plus a small service fee. Just let us know your preferences."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you inspect for guest damage?",
    answer: "Absolutely. We check for damage, missing items, and anything that needs attention before your next guest arrives. We'll notify you immediately of any issues so you can address them or document for Airbnb claims."
  },
  {
    question: "Do you work with property managers?",
    answer: "Yes! We work with several Decatur-area property managers and offer volume pricing for multiple properties. Consistent quality, reliable scheduling, and direct communication make us a trusted partner for vacation rental management."
  }
];

